#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:1
msgid "VTK::IOXDMF2"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:3
msgid ""
"The IO/Xdmf2 directory contains a reduced distribution of the xdmf2/vtk (pv "
"branch) source tree with only the library source code needed by VTK.  It is "
"not a submodule; the actual content is part of our source tree and changes "
"can be made and committed directly."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:9
msgid ""
"We update from upstream using Git's \"subtree\" merge strategy.  A special "
"branch contains commits of upstream xdmf2/vtk snapshots and nothing else.  "
"No Git ref points explicitly to the head of this branch, but it is merged "
"into our history."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:14
msgid ""
"Update xdmf2/vtk from upstream as follows.  Create a local branch to "
"explicitly reference the upstream snapshot branch head:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:17
msgid "git branch xdmf2vtk-upstream f40916ae"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:19
msgid "Use a temporary directory to checkout the branch:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:21
msgid ""
"mkdir xdmf2vtk-tmp  cd xdmf2vtk-tmp  git init  git pull .. xdmf2vtk-"
"upstream  rm -rf *"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:27
msgid ""
"Now place the (reduced) xdmf2/vtk content in this directory.  See "
"instructions shown by"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:30
msgid "git log f40916ae"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:32
msgid ""
"for help extracting the content from the upstream tarball.  Then run the "
"following commands to commit the new version.  Substitute the appropriate "
"date and version number:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:36
msgid "git add --all"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:38
msgid ""
"GIT_AUTHOR_NAME='XDMF Developers' \\  GIT_AUTHOR_EMAIL='xdmf@lists.kitware."
"com' \\  GIT_AUTHOR_DATE='2012-08-01 16:14:03 -0500' \\  git commit -m "
"'xdmf2/vtk 2012-08-01 (reduced)' &&  git commit --amend"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:0
msgid "<br />\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:0
msgid "\\\\\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:44
msgid ""
"Edit the commit message to describe the procedure used to obtain the "
"content. Then push the changes back up to the main local repository:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:47
msgid "git push .. HEAD:xdmf2vtk-upstream  cd ..  rm -rf xdmf2vtk-tmp"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:51
msgid "Create a topic in the main repository on which to perform the update:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:53
msgid "git checkout -b update-xdmf2 master"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:55
msgid "Merge the xdmf2vtk-upstream branch as a subtree:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:57
msgid ""
"git merge -s recursive -X subtree=IO/Xdmf2 \\            xdmf2vtk-upstream"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:60
msgid ""
"If there are conflicts, resolve them and commit.  Build and test the tree.  "
"Commit any additional changes needed to succeed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:63
msgid "Finally, run"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:65
msgid "git rev-parse --short=8 xdmf2vtk-upstream"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../modules/vtk-modules/IO/Xdmf2/README.md:67
msgid ""
"to get the commit from which the xdmf2vtk-upstream branch must be started on "
"the next update.  Edit the \"git branch xdmf2vtk-upstream\" line above to "
"record it, and commit this file."
msgstr ""
